<div class="table-container shadow">
	<h1 class="text-center">The company logo database and API</h1>
	<p>CompaniesLogo provides access to the logos of <strong>13195</strong> companies in different formats and sizes. Most publicly listed companies including stocks and ETFs are present in the database.</strong></p>
	<p>In regular intervals, typically every 3 months the database is manually checked to determine if the logo of a company has been changed.</p>
	<p>The website's logo database can be accessed through our company logo API, allowing you to automatically display up-to-date logos of companies on your websites or Apps.</p>
	<p class="text-center">
		<a href="/stock-logo-api/">
			<button class="contact-button">Learn more about our company logo API ➜</button></a>
			&nbsp;
